  h2 About this map

  h3 Privacy
  p The 'Find nearest offices' tool will request access to your current location.  If you grant access the coordinates of your current location will be used to find the 10 closest USFWS offices in the Southeast Region.  This location data is only used on the client (in your web browser) and is never transimitted back to the Service, or stored in any way.

